data.description: SELLER WANTS THIS GONE! MAKE THEM AN OFFER. Relax and settle into your new home, where you can indulge in the serene lake views and observe golfers at the 8th Hole of the beautiful Lush Executive 18-hole Golf Course. This desirable 55+ Gated Community of Kings Gate offers an ideal setting with a lot of activities, new friends and lots of fun! Inside the home, you'll find a well-designed layout with 2 bedrooms, a den, and 2 bathrooms, along with a 2-car garage. The split bedroom floor plan provides flexibility, allowing you to accommodate overnight guests or utilize the extra space as an office or craft room. For those who love cooking, the spacious kitchen boasts a breakfast area and a prep sink in the island. The dining area connects to the living room, offering space for entertaining family and friends. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet and access to the lanai. The master bathroom complements the suite with a garden tub and a walk-in shower. Additionally, the 2-car garage provides space for your tinkering projects. The homeowners' association (HOA) takes care of yard maintenance, allowing you to make the most of the Florida sun and engage in other activities.
